He never loved me.

805
01:09:24,916 --> 01:09:25,950
Maia?

806
01:09:26,616 --> 01:09:28,119
Who is this?

807
01:09:28,252 --> 01:09:29,754
He wanted a son.

808
01:09:30,487 --> 01:09:32,056
He needed a son.

809
01:09:33,824 --> 01:09:36,160
