when darkness reigns!
[screaming]

930
01:17:38,942 --> 01:17:42,814
Family, hearth,
straw and stone!

931
01:17:42,946 --> 01:17:44,982
He prepares the vessel!

932
01:17:45,115 --> 01:17:48,585
[group] Family, hearth,
straw and stone...

933
