Find him, Maia.

941
01:18:34,598 --> 01:18:37,167
[hissing]

942
01:18:43,574 --> 01:18:45,576
[Joseph]
Welcome, baby Lucian,

943
01:18:45,709 --> 01:18:49,980
bringer of light,
lord of fire and blood.

944
01:18:51,248 --> 01:18:56,353
We charge you now, Robert,
to raise him well,

945
01:18:56,487 --> 01:19:02,159
