981
01:23:36,333 --> 01:23:38,002
<i>Blood,</i>

982
01:23:38,136 --> 01:23:42,807
<i>tears will spill forth</i>
<i>from his mouth.</i>

983
01:23:43,975 --> 01:23:49,981
